<h2>Syteg SSP Wordpress plugin</h2>
<p>The wordpress users can easily add Live chat widget to a website, apply customized settings and use it free of charge.</p>
<p>To start using this plugin you should do the following steps: </p>
<ol>
    <li style="line-height: 30px">Create an account on  <a href="https://syteg.com/register" target="_blank">syteg.com</a></li>
    <li style="line-height: 30px">Go to SSP panel <img style="height: 30px; vertical-align: middle" src="https://syteg.com/images/plugins/go_to_panel.png" /></li>
    <li style="line-height: 30px">Get External Chat line number that you are going to use <img style="height: 30px; vertical-align: middle" src="https://syteg.com/images/plugins/chat_line_number.png" /> (You can find your chat line number in Services & Employees Tab.)</li>
    <li style="line-height: 30px">Set up the service in plugin</li>
    <li style="line-height: 30px">Sign in to <a href="https://call-center.syteg.com/new">Syteg SSP panel</a>, and start using free Live chat.</li>
</ol>
<p>If you have difficulties in using our services - please check tutorial in SSP panel or submit a support ticket on <a href="https://syteg.com/support-center.html" target="_blank">syteg.com</a></p>
<p>Syteg SSP Team</p>